        <updateDate>2019-07-23T20:27:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>21 to Buy Act</b></p> <p>This bill generally prohibits a licensed gun dealer, manufacturer, importer, or collector from selling or transferring a shotgun or rifle to an individual who is under age 21.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
